{"tid":1004434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普簽行政命令　促政府承包商用「美國製造」","createTime":"2019-02-01T12:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T04:21:19.000Z","uid":141151,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d8e2e0b6651ea23b9f6a9d64cdcb09223708333e","tid":1004434,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T12:18:50.000Z","msg":"特朗普簽行政命令　促政府承包商用「美國製造」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190201/bkn-20190201071450894-0201_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190201%2Fbkn-20190201071450894-0201_00972_001.html&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxsj2djVMnfBKxsW1BXeekzK0%3D&h=c9d55885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190201/bkn-20190201071450894-0201_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普周四（1月31日）簽署一項行政命令，旨在鼓勵政府承包商採購美國製造的物料和產品，以響應政府促進美國製造業的努力。 <br />\n<br />\n該項行政命令要求聯邦部門，鼓勵接受聯邦撥款承建基建項目的公司，使用美國製造的鐵、鋼、鋁和水泥等。特朗普在白宮橢圓形辦公室簽署命令時表示：「我們希望美國的道路、橋樑、鐵路和所有其他東西，都是用美國的鐵、鋼和混凝土，以美國人的手來建成。」 <br />\n<br />\n特朗普在入主白宮之初，曾簽下一項類似的行政命令，要求聯邦部門盡可能採購美國製造的產品。"},{"pid":"309e88f2dc8a4b0d39f26db6e6d497a46688e9fe","tid":1004434,"uid":41992,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T12:23:02.000Z","msg":"支那唔賣料比美國 <br />\n<br />\n中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"356fc63e370ba4968e006dc2c22495a29c0cd04f","tid":1004434,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:15:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52fd96eb1d759414ef145095adc73c260ed4c1f9","tid":1004434,"uid":18127,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T03:34:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6a38ee6a6f49b087b227e5b5c6e0866dbe05455","tid":1004434,"uid":34641,"like":0,"